      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire an investment-grade vehicle in truly pristine condition. This unit has been curated and maintained to the most exacting standards, exhibiting no discernible wear and offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original showroom state. A rare find for the discerning collector who demands uncompromising mechanical and aesthetic integrity.",
